Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have another coffee, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a request!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A request?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, this is something I should solve on my own,{lit this is just my problem}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have no right to ask you for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But please, just hear me out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's all I need to do, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about my uncle. His name was Sekitani Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me remember what he told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I skipped a few details.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain things from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle went to India seven years ago, and nobody has heard from him since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was little, I was very attached to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He would answer any question I asked, no matter how crazy it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as if there was nothing he didn't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in kindergarten, I heard that he was in the Classics Club,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I became interested in it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's because "Classics" sounded similar to the "candy sticks" I loved at home.{lit vinegar-kelp}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a really bad pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I asked him about the Classics Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the one and only question he avoided answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He avoided it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I threw a huge tantrum, and eventually he relented.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard his answer, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it was because it was scary or because it was depressing, but I cried my eyes out.{if too long, use "...because his answer was scary or depressing,"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You cried...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, I remember my mother came running in surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but my uncle didn't even try to calm me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was such a big shock that I can't remember anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But back when I entered junior high, I couldn't stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he try to dodge the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he try to calm me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done everything I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Though we drifted apart from the Sekitanis, I still tried to stay in touch as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter what I do, I can't remember what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when I started at Kamiyama High, I felt like the Classics Club was my last hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the "personal thing" you were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't know that the Classics Club was on the verge of being disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked the teachers, but none of them remember
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened 45 years ago, when my uncle attended the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Why did you come to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can solve mysteries that I can't even fathom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the locked door, the library book,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and the secret club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know that you'll be able to lead me to the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You really shouldn't overestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just dumb luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me count on that luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You could say that this mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is at the core of Chitanda Eru's very life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you really think a low-energy person like me would want to be responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So why just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely there are other people you could talk to as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Many hands make light work, right?{人海戦術, replace with idiom if possible}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ask all your friends to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the kind of person who just goes around revealing her past to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,something I can discuss with just anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm really asking a lot of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I shouldn't be getting you mixed up in my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not be as friendly as my uncle, but you answer my questions too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please accept my deepest apologies for being unfriendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might've seen something of my uncle in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,High school lasts for three years, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more than enough time to investigate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to remember my uncle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,before he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Before he's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone goes missing{lit life-or-death is unclear} for seven years,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,they're considered legally dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle's family wants closure as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They're of modest means, but they've planned a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to find out what he told me back then...{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And prepare myself for the funeral, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not like you have anything better to do, right?{the letter}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take on this responsibility for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't say that I'll take on your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll keep all this in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I hear anything that might point you in the right direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any trouble interpreting the clues,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can assist you with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can agree to those terms, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll be able to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though people say high school life is colorful,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it isn't all fun and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For example, we have exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At Kamiyama High, midterms have begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All club activities are put on hold during the exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and needless to say, that includes the Classics Club as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We didn't do much to begin with, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so not a lot has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We probably could've kept meeting in the clubroom as usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but with no key available we didn't have much choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, pens down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, the midterms are over... Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:08:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am writing to you from Istanbul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A few things went wrong when I arrived, so I'm currently stuck in the Japanese consulate and haven't seen much of the city yet.{split?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm really enjoying this trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure that ten years from now, I'll be able to look back on these days without regret.{i'm really unsure about this but his reaction shows that this line isn't supposed to be alright}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By the way, how's the Classics Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Has anyone else joined?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's one other thing on my mind, so I thought I'd better mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will you be making an anthology?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Classics Club used to release an anthology every year at the culture fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you still doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If so, you might be wondering what you need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Classics Club's prior anthologies aren't kept in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should be able to find them in the clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's this unused medicine safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The back issues are in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I arrive in Pristina, I'll give you a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Greetings, Oreki Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A medicine safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't have chosen a better time to tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought the letter with me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's in a medicine safe, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I haven't seen anything like that here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But then what about the anthologies? The anthologies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Chill out, Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Chi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda, all she said was that the medicine safe is in the clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister graduated two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The clubroom has changed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! So that's what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you know which room it was two years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked our club advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it was the biology prep room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you really did your homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I just took the most efficient approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Such enthusiasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the meaning of the word "enthusiasm".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what about Fukube?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That sew-and-sew?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He was going on about taking a sneak peek at some summer fashion thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd locked the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you interested in joining the News Poster Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the News Poster Club's room, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That smell... Cologne?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or rather... Air freshener?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the president of the Classics Club, Chitanda Eru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Tougaito from Class 3-E, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember seeing you last year at the Manninbashis'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,At the Manninbashis'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment, would you happen to be one of the Chitandas from Kanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You've been a great help to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, please, the feeling's mutual...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, a Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why's he so tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:13:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! We heard the Classics Club's old anthologies were being kept here in the biology prep room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This used to be the Classics Club's room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Oh, right. I think it was when I was a first-year student, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So would you happen to know anything about the anthologies?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but they have to be in here somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let us look for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but like I just said, they're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then stick around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but you'll have to look somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But we heard that they were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't find them here, we'll have to search the entire school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The entire school? That's out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer not to let outsiders in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No offense, but this is a classroom first and a clubroom second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibara Mayaka from the Classics Club.{<3}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take a look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't make a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the other club members?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They're on break today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about what to put in the June issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the Kami High Monthly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It has quite a history. We're nearing the 500th issue, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tougaito,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,did anything get moved around when you switched clubrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, we had to carry a few cardboard boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Cardboard boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The tricky part would be getting to it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's give this guy a good shake and see what falls out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry, but there's so much stuff in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that it'd take ages for us to look through it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask our club advisor
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to help us give it a more thorough search.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to make a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the only lead we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take full responsibility for returning everything to the way it—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about your thorough search!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your anthologies aren't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that? Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're after what's in the medicine safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The anthologies are supposedly in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we need. No skin off your back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, we have things we need to do in the library right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,so if you should happen to find the anthologies after we've left,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd be grateful if you could bring them to the earth science prep room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I find them, I'll bring them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't introduced yourself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we waiting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To save energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Tougaito's family famous for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're quite well-known in the field of junior high school education.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people from their family work in education, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what we have here.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the anthologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Oreki, what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit of blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackmail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibara,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,can you keep a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tell me not to talk about it, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's start from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When Tougaito came out of that room, he was clearly wary of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How about inside the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The windows were open and he had the fan turned on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but from that position the papers on the desk were almost blown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to air out the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did he want to air out the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,why would he lock the door and set up an infrared sen—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What are you talking about? What infrared sensor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There were these tiny boxes on the corridor walls that I hadn't seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that gadget with an antenna in the room was the receiver,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,then it must have been set up to alert him when someone passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you figure that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a guess based on the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would he take so much care to start airing out the room
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as someone passed by?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To clear out a smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He also smelled of air freshener.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What smell would he want to cover up that badly?{lit keep people from knowing}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobacco, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The heir of a family famous in the field of education
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't allow anyone to find him smoking illegally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, if Chitanda didn't have a cold, she would've smelled it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,where were the anthologies, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In the medicine safe, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,O-re-ki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not making fun of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The medicine safe was under that home-made table.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he must've been hiding his smokes and lighter in there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he panicked when I suggested
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,getting a teacher involved in the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm as average as they come.{there's something wrong. chitanda too quiet}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a sunflower!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we found the old anthologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how they look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{ib}This one's forty years old, so does that mean it was written by hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's wrong, Chitanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{sa}Nah, they probably printed it with a mimeograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{sa}Or in other words, a cyclostyle.{lit. to be exact, mimeographed. he uses a different word for the same thing ガリ版 - 謄写版} It was invented in the late 19th century.{Meiji era}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{sa}I doubt the school would have had a photocopier during the 1970s.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:20:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oreki...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{sa}Look, this one was photocopied...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{ib}I see...{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hyouka".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Issue number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I found back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought it to my uncle
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and asked him what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You remembered?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something in here that has to do with my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Something happened 45 years ago in the Classics Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"And so, this year the culture fair has come once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One year has passed since Sekitani left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The year that he began as a hero and finished as a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The battles he fought, the sacrifices he made,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the smiles he shared
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,will all be carried along by the river of time, into the distant past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not something meant to be remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing even close to an epic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And as it loses all subjectivity,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it all becomes part of the classics, as per the rules of historic perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One day we too will just be classic literature on someone's shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,October 13, 1964. Kooriyama Youko."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The year before that was 45 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that the Sekitani mentioned there was my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it was that he told me, it was related to the Classics Club as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's all right now, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't remember what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he tell me that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to my uncle 45 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you investigate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It says right there that it shouldn't be remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I find out something I never wanted to know?{lit if i investigated it may end badly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things in the world best left forgotten, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even things from 45 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As it says here:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"It all becomes part of the classics, as per the rules of historic perspective."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already in the past{happened}.{ so it's okay to talk about}.{時効}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to look into it further, this article refers to the previous year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.24,0:23:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So why not just check the first issue—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.49,0:23:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The first issue is the only one that's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.22,0:25:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time:
